{
  "stem": "18186.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 261.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So at that time, when-- when it started, when it came to our-- our-- to liquidate our ghetto, the night before I worked as a-- I was babysitting for a Ukrainian family at that time.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Outside of the ghetto?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Outside the ghetto, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "This went through the-- legally-- I did not sneak out to do that.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the-- they came that day in the afternoon.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They came to us to-- to ask for horse and buggy.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And my-- the family that I babysit for, they had-- they were farmers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they worked on the farm, and not too far from the house.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I said, no.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I don't know anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that was Ukrainian people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I don't know anything, but the people on the farm.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I guess they went there, and they told them for why they need it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then they came back, and they send me home.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then-- and that was the end of it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "I never went back.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "I mean that-- that was the night when they came, and they-- that-- that liquidating-- they liquidated our ghetto.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So again, we in the house, we-- me and my-- and my-- and my mother and my sisters and brothers, and other people, the people that lived in that house decided to go up in the attic, and take the-- we had like a-- to going up to the attic, we had a-- a--",
      "word_count": 54
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A ladder.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we took the ladder with us, so in case they're gonna-- they're gonna-- gonna come up, they'll see we don't-- that nobody is there.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But-- and also we knew from others in other towns that if-- let's say it happened one night, and whoever survived that night-- they-- they didn't bother anymore.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
